                <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:8pt; line-height:108%; font-size:11pt;"><strong><span style="font-family:Nunito;">12.</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:Nunito;">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><u><span style="font-family:Nunito;">The App / Mobile Devices</span></u></strong></p>
